<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>__WFI();<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Select<sp/>Sleep<sp/>mode<sp/>entry<sp/>:<sp/>Request<sp/>Wait<sp/>For<sp/>Interrupt</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
