        <name>port_system_systick_resume</name>
        <param>
          <type>void</type>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Resume Tick increment. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The SysTick timer is the source of time base. It is used to generate interrupts at regular time intervals. Once this function is called, the SysTick interrupt will be enabled and so Tick increment is resumed.</para>
<para><blockquote><para><bold>TODO alumnos Version 4:</bold></para>
<para>✅ 1. Copy the following code in the file <ref refid="stm32f4__system_8c" kindref="compound">stm32f4_system.c</ref>. <linebreak/>
</para>
</blockquote></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="port__system_8h_1a2dca6b2c8ee48c36828b323f42c47fc8" kindref="member">port_system_systick_resume</ref>()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>SysTick-&gt;CTRL<sp/>|=<sp/>SysTick_CTRL_TICKINT_Msk;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
        </detaileddescription>
